{"tid":1136363,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：37.8%小學生過去一年曾遇校園欺凌　14.3%被打　4.8%欲尋死","createTime":"2019-05-03T03:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T07:20:39.000Z","uid":160807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0d7f0a89de834d85e87a6ec881d3b51254f391fe","tid":1136363,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2732433/org/fe6e2705a13644dc91256e4a4349ff64.jpg/_mVLHlmgjMzFPtdobCH5VbdiCYrZBUn3hLdVZ4S3VWc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2732433%2Forg%2Ffe6e2705a13644dc91256e4a4349ff64.jpg%2F_mVLHlmgjMzFPtdobCH5VbdiCYrZBUn3hLdVZ4S3VWc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=b171cb6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學生校園欺凌個案不容忽視。一項調查發現，37.8%學童曾於過去一年遭遇同輩欺凌，14.3%受訪者試過被拳打腳踢、19.8%曾遭杯葛排擠。不過，19%學童遇欺凌時會不知所措，亦有10.4%及4.8%受訪者因而抗拒上學及萌生自殺念頭。<br />\n<br />\n有專家表示，不少家長或輕視事件，建議父母冷靜處理，亦切忌武斷，宜有商有量解決僵局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2732434/org/e49515ac2bd3f564195a3e1dafc03c29.jpg/GSg3DN_9k_UwBs3Z28KsEfDaCxEtDNV4RXHjvUVx470?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2732434%2Forg%2Fe49515ac2bd3f564195a3e1dafc03c29.jpg%2FGSg3DN_9k_UwBs3Z28KsEfDaCxEtDNV4RXHjvUVx470%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=15baf663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>約8%平均一個月遇過5次或以上</strong><br />\n<br />\n獅子山青年商會聯同香港家庭調解協會，於今年2月至4月期間，成功在全港各區抽樣訪問604名小一至小六學生，調查結果顯示，37.8%受訪者表示過去一年曾遇欺凌事件，當中8.1％學童更平均一個月遇過5次或以上。<br />\n<br />\n欺凌形式方面，43%受訪學童表示曾被起花名，亦不乏身體接觸及言語欺凌，近24%學童表示曾被人故意推撞或用腳絆倒；14.3％受訪者則表示在過去一年曾經被人拳打腳踢；另亦有26.9%受訪者曾遭遇言語欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n社交欺凌亦見嚴重，22.5%學童曾在過去一年被人散播謠言、另19.8%曾被杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一成受欺凌者抗拒上學</strong><br />\n<br />\n遭遇校園欺凌時，31.3%受訪小學生表示感到憤怒，10.4%因而抗拒上學，亦有4.8％受訪者萌生自殺念頭。調查又顯示，19%學童表明不知如何應對，12.4%則坦言曾向人求助但問題未見改善。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>家庭調解協會：家長要冷靜、忌武斷行事</strong><br />\n<br />\n家庭調解協會總幹事梁淑瑜表示，凡重覆地遭受一個或多個學生的負面及惡意對待，已可被視為欺凌行為，當中最常見包括推撞及拳打腳踢等身體接觸，又或起別名及出言恐嚇等言語傷害；亦有散播謠言等社交欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n她續指，中心以往接觸過不少欺凌個案，有家長曾不當處理及輕視事件，甚至覺得是欺凌者自身有問題。<br />\n<br />\n梁淑瑜建議，如子女遇欺凌事件，家長首要冷靜，切忌武斷，宜切身處地解對方感受，再鼓勵雙方調解，學習有商有量處理僵局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/322882/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-37-8-%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E6%9B%BE%E9%81%87%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C-14-3-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93-4-8-%E6%AC%B2%E5%B0%8B%E6%AD%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F322882%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-37-8-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2581%2587%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C-14-3-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593-4-8-%25E6%25AC%25B2%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%25AD%25BB&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=55ec6c3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/322882/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-37-8-%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E6%9B%BE%E9%81%87%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C-14-3-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93-4-8-%E6%AC%B2%E5%B0%8B%E6%AD%BB</a>"},{"pid":"114906d6bd93729434098ba0b26a397bcbcb894e","tid":1136363,"uid":80814,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"諗返我中學都叫好彩雖然啲格串柒柒又中二病, 一條毒撚又唔係叻走去睇唔起班MK, 喺屬會搞到被人排, 但都喺自己班識到朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf81556e3fffc7e507b3da703a26c9886176fc3","tid":1136363,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:24:48.000Z","msg":"有時唔知點幫, 因為有啲細路遲熟, 有啲細路早熟, 早熟嗰啲會嫌遲熟嗰啲聽大人話嘅係傻仔, 同埋又好興笑人樣衰同低B, 話咁樣只係話吓, 有啲心理質素強啲會反擊, 笑返人轉頭, 有啲就真係硬食哂。有時有啲細路遲熟, 又會喺班度做乖仔搏班教師注意到連教師都覺得煩, 當個教師都公開笑佢, 其他學生都會加入。"},{"pid":"b49ad9ba97b4f43b033aa6540b399d048261d557","tid":1136363,"uid":49918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"984d5fc32168de438a91bfea2c5643843aad4acc","tid":1136363,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:35:33.000Z","msg":"唔識用拳頭建立自己威信嘅小朋友應該被淘汰"},{"pid":"44a6d154379f53388d37fa1e14e7fab57337f9b9","tid":1136363,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:36:43.000Z","msg":"其實中小學真係好多打交case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9379af8085cadccb05b1844fbf761c467242bde7","tid":1136363,"uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b49ad9ba97b4f43b033aa6540b399d048261d557","tid":1136363,"uid":49918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:37:34.000Z","msg":"有咩咁奇 香港校園欺凌比率世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170421/bkn-20170421132001803-0421_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170421%2Fbkn-20170421132001803-0421_00822_001.html&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=b3e7a904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170421/bkn-20170421132001803-0421_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d0fb7a13a999899c63fe89a300b6bf1aac3be92e","tid":1136363,"uid":77222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"中學呢"},{"pid":"2825b62ba4c014e58789ea91a11aaf10c55edfd7","tid":1136363,"uid":51625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"香港人....真係好邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有人快啲出嚟表態搞對抗，如果唔係將來自己嘅仔女不幸中招嗰陣唔好喊"},{"pid":"7050db7112d192048965cbaa6ca8a6d6e03d8220","tid":1136363,"uid":216080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c903583441e0fc9584c0da19b4e603ede0693ce5","tid":1136363,"uid":216080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:48:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6807712e05417c904a4fa52efd69e367a95dde4e","tid":1136363,"uid":165336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"其實有學返既圬方就係有呢d野嫁啦<br />\n有d人天性就係咁撚仆街<br />\n又有d人係父母仆街,係屋企俾人打完<br />\n咪返學打d唔夠打自己既人囉<br />\n最慘係果d屋企又俾人打<br />\n又天生體質差返學都俾人打果d<br />\n姐係我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計我話最好一家一社工,一校一警長<br />\n一層一警察,全部睇撚到實哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a4ba707291caed801458664cb1fd1742abc76e","tid":1136363,"uid":216080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f4754c99c9e4e8f4a977be1930e6d8d0e6a8503","tid":1136363,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5a4ba707291caed801458664cb1fd1742abc76e","tid":1136363,"uid":216080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d7f0a89de834d85e87a6ec881d3b51254f391fe","tid":1136363,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2732433/org/fe6e2705a13644dc91256e4a4349ff64.jpg/_mVLHlmgjMzFPtdobCH5VbdiCYrZBUn3hLdVZ4S3VWc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2732433%2Forg%2Ffe6e2705a13644dc91256e4a4349ff64.jpg%2F_mVLHlmgjMzFPtdobCH5VbdiCYrZBUn3hLdVZ4S3VWc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=b171cb6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學生校園欺凌個案不容忽視。一項調查發現，37.8%學童曾於過去一年遭遇同輩欺凌，14.3%受訪者試過被拳打腳踢、19.8%曾遭杯葛排擠。不過，19%學童遇欺凌時會不知所措，亦有10.4%及4.8%受訪者因而抗拒上學及萌生自殺念頭。<br />\n<br />\n有專家表示，不少家長或輕視事件，建議父母冷靜處理，亦切忌武斷，宜有商有量解決僵局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2732434/org/e49515ac2bd3f564195a3e1dafc03c29.jpg/GSg3DN_9k_UwBs3Z28KsEfDaCxEtDNV4RXHjvUVx470?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2732434%2Forg%2Fe49515ac2bd3f564195a3e1dafc03c29.jpg%2FGSg3DN_9k_UwBs3Z28KsEfDaCxEtDNV4RXHjvUVx470%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=15baf663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>約8%平均一個月遇過5次或以上</strong><br />\n<br />\n獅子山青年商會聯同香港家庭調解協會，於今年2月至4月期間，成功在全港各區抽樣訪問604名小一至小六學生，調查結果顯示，37.8%受訪者表示過去一年曾遇欺凌事件，當中8.1％學童更平均一個月遇過5次或以上。<br />\n<br />\n欺凌形式方面，43%受訪學童表示曾被起花名，亦不乏身體接觸及言語欺凌，近24%學童表示曾被人故意推撞或用腳絆倒；14.3％受訪者則表示在過去一年曾經被人拳打腳踢；另亦有26.9%受訪者曾遭遇言語欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n社交欺凌亦見嚴重，22.5%學童曾在過去一年被人散播謠言、另19.8%曾被杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一成受欺凌者抗拒上學</strong><br />\n<br />\n遭遇校園欺凌時，31.3%受訪小學生表示感到憤怒，10.4%因而抗拒上學，亦有4.8％受訪者萌生自殺念頭。調查又顯示，19%學童表明不知如何應對，12.4%則坦言曾向人求助但問題未見改善。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>家庭調解協會：家長要冷靜、忌武斷行事</strong><br />\n<br />\n家庭調解協會總幹事梁淑瑜表示，凡重覆地遭受一個或多個學生的負面及惡意對待，已可被視為欺凌行為，當中最常見包括推撞及拳打腳踢等身體接觸，又或起別名及出言恐嚇等言語傷害；亦有散播謠言等社交欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n她續指，中心以往接觸過不少欺凌個案，有家長曾不當處理及輕視事件，甚至覺得是欺凌者自身有問題。<br />\n<br />\n梁淑瑜建議，如子女遇欺凌事件，家長首要冷靜，切忌武斷，宜切身處地解對方感受，再鼓勵雙方調解，學習有商有量處理僵局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/322882/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-37-8-%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E6%9B%BE%E9%81%87%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C-14-3-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93-4-8-%E6%AC%B2%E5%B0%8B%E6%AD%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F322882%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-37-8-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2581%2587%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C-14-3-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593-4-8-%25E6%25AC%25B2%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%25AD%25BB&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=55ec6c3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/322882/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-37-8-%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E6%9B%BE%E9%81%87%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C-14-3-%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93-4-8-%E6%AC%B2%E5%B0%8B%E6%AD%BB</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:06:47.000Z","msg":"其實好多時班教師嘅態度都會影響到學生會唔會被蝦同排斥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e3ff6aa8ef7a3eba375c25a129391e443a3a69","tid":1136363,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"想死既肯定只止4.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c839340ef4422b8d719984ee2b0d78eed5635b","tid":1136363,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"咁多支那人生一堆又唔教 梗係多欺凌啦<br />\n以前間小學好似都收左兩個弱智成日比人欺凌<br />\n兩個應該都似係中度弱智<br />\n中度弱智根本完全跟唔上教學的進度<br />\n一個純粹係傻傻地好和平<br />\n另一個痴痴地線成日周圍屌人老母<br />\n前者比人恰都會有同學出面幫佢<br />\n後者比人恰真係完全冇人理<br />\n成日都搞到佢好激動要老師用武力捉住佢先解決到<br />\n真係唔明父母點解要送佢地去正常學校讀書"},{"pid":"c4eec14bae7cee9a4a0165a086063639876dc531","tid":1136363,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"被人嗌兩下死肥仔算唔算欺凌?"}]}